      "Reyleigh. Random vector: Joint distributions, Marginal and conditional distributions, Moments,",
      "Independence of random variables, Covariance, Correlation, Functions of random variables. Law of",
      "Large Numbers: Weak law of large numbers, Levy’s Central limit theorem (i.i.d. finite variance case),",
      "Normal and Poisson approximations to Binomial.",
      "Statistics",
      "Unit - 3 9 Hours",
      "Introduction: Population, Sample, Parameters.",
      "Point Estimation: Method of moments, Maximum likelihood estimation, Unbiasedness, Consistency.",
      "Interval Estimation: Confidence interval.",
