      "CS 404: Formal Language and Automata Theory 3 0 0 3",
      "Introduction: Basic Mathematical Objects: Sets, Logic, Functions, Relations, Strings, Alphabets,",
      "Languages. Mathematical Induction: Inductive proofs, Principles; Recursive Definitions; Set Notation.",
      "Finite Automata and Regular Expressions: Finite State systems, Regular Languages & Regular",
      "Expressions, Deterministic Finite Automata; Nondeterministic Finite Automata, Kleene’ Theorem;",
      "Two-way Finite Automata, Finite Automata with output, Properties of Regular Sets: The Pumping",
