      "Algorithm for Fault simulation: Parallel, Deductive and Concurrent Techniques , Roth’s Test -",
      "Detect Algorithm; Critical Path Tracing.",
      "Test generation for combinational circuits: Boolean difference, D -algorithm, PODEM,",
      "Exhaustive, random and weighted test pattern generation; aliasing and its effect on fault coverage.",
      "PLA testing: Cross-point fault model, test generation, easily testable designs.",
