      "in multiple dielectrics – Boundary conditions, Poisson’s and Laplace’s equations, Capacitance, Energy",
      "density, Applications.",
      "MAGNETOSTATICS: Lorentz force, magnetic field intensity (H) – Biot–Savart’s Law – Ampere’s Circuit",
