      "Text-Book 1.“Digital Design”, Mano Morris, 5th Edition, Pearson Education, 2005. Reference Books 1.“Digital Logic and Computer Design”, Mano Morris, 3rd Edition, Pearson Education, 2005. 2.“Digital Electronics Practice Using Integrated Circuits”, Jain and Anand, TMH, 2004 3.“Logic and Computer Design Fundamentals”, Kime Charles, Pearson Education, 2004. 4.“Digital Circuits and Logic Design”, Lee Samual, PHI, 1998. 5.“Digital Fundamentals”, Floyd and Jain, Pearson Education, 2006.",
